{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":442558,"duration_api_ms":442832,"ttft_ms":4207,"num_turns":48,"result":"Review complete for CP00-514 — verdict **PASS_WITH_FINDINGS** (0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2, 2 P3; non-blocking for pack and goal closeout).

